{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "kqm6ncbbnbo",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KQM6ncbBNBo",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "There.",
      "zh": "好了。",
      "ja": "できた。",
      "time": "00:01:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What do you think?",
      "zh": "你覺得怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "どう思う？",
      "time": "00:01:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's perfect.",
      "zh": "很完美。",
      "ja": "完璧だ。",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And...",
      "zh": "然後...",
      "ja": "それから...",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "they're...",
      "zh": "它們已經...",
      "ja": "それらは...",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "posted.",
      "zh": "發布了。",
      "ja": "投稿した。",
      "time": "00:01:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're gonna do that every time?",
      "zh": "你每次都要這樣做嗎？",
      "ja": "毎回そうするの？",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How else does everyone supposed to like what you make?",
      "zh": "不然大家怎麼會喜歡你做的東西？",
      "ja": "そうしなきゃみんなが君の作品を好きになるわけないだろ？",
      "time": "00:01:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I think in like them all they want as long as they buy something too.",
      "zh": "我想他們都願意，只要他們也買點東西。",
      "ja": "みんな買い物もすればいいと思ってるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Iceman Carpet has over a million followers.",
      "zh": "Iceman Carpet 有超過一百萬粉絲。",
      "ja": "アイスマン・カーペットは100万人以上のフォロワーがいる。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My buddy sells a lot.",
      "zh": "我朋友賣得很多。",
      "ja": "友達はたくさん売ってる。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How many followers do I have?",
      "zh": "我有多少粉絲？",
      "ja": "僕のフォロワーはどれくらい？",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:01:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Not that many.",
      "zh": "不多。",
      "ja": "そんなに多くない。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's a good thing I have you then.",
      "zh": "那還好我有你。",
      "ja": "それなら君がいてくれてよかった。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-oh.",
      "zh": "糟了。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Uh-oh.",
      "zh": "糟了。",
      "ja": "やばい。",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's up?",
      "zh": "怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうした？",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We went over time.",
      "zh": "我們超時了。",
      "ja": "時間オーバーした。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I told you to watch the clock.",
      "zh": "我叫你注意時間。",
      "ja": "時計を見るように言っただろ。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We'll get you back back.",
      "zh": "我們會帶你回去的。",
      "ja": "すぐに戻るよ。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And your gloves.",
      "zh": "還有你的手套。",
      "ja": "そして手袋も。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Mr. Jacobs, I hate to give you bad news this close to the holidays,",
      "zh": "Jacobs 先生，這麼接近假期我不想帶來壞消息，",
      "ja": "ジェイコブズさん、ホリデーシーズン直前に悪い知らせを伝えたくはないのですが、",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "but with your debt to asset ratio,",
      "zh": "但以你的負債資產比，",
      "ja": "あなたの負債資産比率では、",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "the bank is unable to grant you loan.",
      "zh": "銀行無法批准你的貸款。",
      "ja": "銀行はローンを承認できません。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Feel free to call with any questions.",
      "zh": "有任何問題請隨時來電。",
      "ja": "質問があれば遠慮なく電話してください。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, wait.",
      "zh": "哦，等等。",
      "ja": "あ、待って。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I forgot to pack your lunch again.",
      "zh": "我又忘了幫你準備午餐。",
      "ja": "またお弁当を詰めるのを忘れた。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I made it last night.",
      "zh": "我昨晚做的。",
      "ja": "昨夜作ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm an amazing kid.",
      "zh": "我真是個了不起的孩子。",
      "ja": "私はすごい子だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You know that?",
      "zh": "你知道嗎？",
      "ja": "知ってる？",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You said you'd fix it.",
      "zh": "你說過你會修好的。",
      "ja": "直すって言ったよね。",
      "time": "00:02:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What's out of fix?",
      "zh": "什麼東西壞了？",
      "ja": "何が壊れたの？",
      "time": "00:02:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Daddy, what's a loan?",
      "zh": "爸爸，什麼是貸款？",
      "ja": "パパ、ローンって何？",
      "time": "00:02:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Well, the bank call?",
      "zh": "嗯，銀行打電話？",
      "ja": "えっと、銀行からの電話？",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You got a text.",
      "zh": "你收到簡訊了。",
      "ja": "メッセージが来たよ。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I should stop reading my text.",
      "zh": "我應該不要一直看簡訊。",
      "ja": "メッセージ読むのやめなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:02:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, loans when someone borrows money from someone else,",
      "zh": "呃，貸款是指有人向別人借錢，",
      "ja": "えっと、ローンは誰かからお金を借りて、",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "and then they got to pay it back later.",
      "zh": "然後必須在之後還回去。",
      "ja": "後で返さなきゃいけないんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do we need money?",
      "zh": "我們需要錢嗎？",
      "ja": "お金が必要？",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No.",
      "zh": "不需要。",
      "ja": "いいえ。",
      "time": "00:02:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then why'd the bank message you?",
      "zh": "那為什麼銀行會發訊息給你？",
      "ja": "じゃあなんで銀行からメッセージが来たの？",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Uh, a little extra would help.",
      "zh": "呃，多一點錢會有幫助。",
      "ja": "ちょっと余分にあれば助かるんだ。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's all.",
      "zh": "就這樣。",
      "ja": "それだけ。",
      "time": "00:02:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Because of the accident?",
      "zh": "是因為那場意外嗎？",
      "ja": "是因為事故嗎？",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll get the hospital bills paid.",
      "zh": "我會付醫院的帳單。",
      "ja": "病院の請求書は払うよ。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll just take a little longer.",
      "zh": "只是會花比較久時間。",
      "ja": "ちょっと時間がかかるだけ。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We'll be fine.",
      "zh": "我們會沒事的。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't need anything for Christmas if it helps.",
      "zh": "如果這樣能幫忙，我聖誕節什麼都不需要。",
      "ja": "それで助かるならクリスマスは何もいらないよ。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, honey.",
      "zh": "哦，親愛的。",
      "ja": "ああ、ハニー。",
      "time": "00:03:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You don't need to worry about that.",
      "zh": "你不需要擔心這個。",
      "ja": "そんなこと気にしなくていいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And I have $114.",
      "zh": "我有114美元。",
      "ja": "僕は114ドル持ってる。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You have a hundred.",
      "zh": "你有一百。",
      "ja": "君は100ドル持ってる。",
      "time": "00:03:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What?",
      "zh": "什麼？",
      "ja": "え？",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you have so much money?",
      "zh": "你怎麼有這麼多錢？",
      "ja": "どうしてそんなにお金があるの？",
      "time": "00:03:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My wants.",
      "zh": "我的零用錢。",
      "ja": "お小遣いだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You saved that much from chores?",
      "zh": "你從家務活存了那麼多？",
      "ja": "家の手伝いでそんなに貯めたの？",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You could have it if you want.",
      "zh": "如果你想要可以給你。",
      "ja": "欲しければあげるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look, sweetheart, you're the sweetest girl in the world,",
      "zh": "看著，親愛的，你是世界上最甜美的女孩，",
      "ja": "ねえ、かわいい子、君は世界で一番優しい女の子だよ、",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "but that's your heart and money.",
      "zh": "但那是你的心和錢。",
      "ja": "でもそれは君の心とお金だ。",
      "time": "00:03:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You keep it.",
      "zh": "你留著吧。",
      "ja": "君が持ってていいよ。",
      "time": "00:03:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You sure?",
      "zh": "你確定嗎？",
      "ja": "本当に？",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sure.",
      "zh": "我確定。",
      "ja": "確かだよ。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hey.",
      "zh": "嘿。",
      "ja": "ねえ。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Welcome, Prime.",
      "zh": "歡迎，Prime。",
      "ja": "ようこそ、プライム。",
      "time": "00:03:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Stick them in the eye.",
      "zh": "戳他們的眼睛。",
      "ja": "目を突け。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Love you, little miss.",
      "zh": "愛你，小小姐。",
      "ja": "愛してるよ、小さなミス。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Love you, too.",
      "zh": "我也愛你。",
      "ja": "僕も愛してる。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Have a good day.",
      "zh": "祝你有美好的一天。",
      "ja": "良い一日を。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ben, is that it?",
      "zh": "Ben，就這樣嗎？",
      "ja": "ベン、それで全部？",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's it.",
      "zh": "就是這樣。",
      "ja": "そうだ。",
      "time": "00:03:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Perfect.",
      "zh": "完美。",
      "ja": "完璧だ。",
      "time": "00:03:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'll put it in the freezer right away.",
      "zh": "我會馬上放進冰箱。",
      "ja": "すぐに冷凍庫に入れるよ。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you so much.",
      "zh": "非常感謝。",
      "ja": "本当にありがとう。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good luck with everything.",
      "zh": "祝你一切順利。",
      "ja": "頑張ってね。",
      "time": "00:03:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, Joe.",
      "zh": "喔，Joe。",
      "ja": "ああ、ジョー。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The chocolate's for tonight?",
      "zh": "巧克力是今晚的嗎？",
      "ja": "チョコレートは今夜のため？",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:03:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just put them on the table over there.",
      "zh": "我剛放在那邊的桌子上。",
      "ja": "さっきあのテーブルに置いたよ。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    }
  ]
}